Requirements for running on Pi

1) build rpi_ws281x
sudo apt-get install scons
cd Rubik/RubikSolver/rpi_ws281x
scons

2) setup python wrapper for rpi
sudo apt-get install python-dev swig
cd python
python setup.py build

3) make RUBIK/run.sh executable
# cd to root of project
chmod +x run.sh

Running:
./run.sh
